      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a driver-focused example of Bavarian engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The high-revving powerplant is paired with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and an M-Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. This chassis is mechanically robust, having received essential rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Vanos system service to maintain peak volumetric efficiency. The suspension retains its signature tactile feedback through a well-sorted multi-link rear setup and MacPherson struts. Finished in Carbon Black, this M3 offers a pure, analog driving experience with the mechanical integrity required for spirited performance.",
