    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's looking for a brand new home! This car has been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape\u2014it's perfect for ziping around town or heading out on a weekend road trip. It drives so smoothly and has been really well-loved. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take it for a spin and see how great it feels behind the wheel!",
